            <thetext>In qooxdoo 3.0, a regression in qx.ui.form.Slider behavior has been introduced. When the slider is activated/deactivated, its knob position is reset to minimum. The &quot;changeValue&quot; event is not emitted, though.

This is observed with Simple and Indigo themes only. Steps to reproduce:
1) Try http://demo.qooxdoo.org/current/demobrowser/#widget~Slider.html
2) Try http://demo.qooxdoo.org/2.1.2/demobrowser/#widget~Slider.html

At least latest Firefox and Chrome are affected.</thetext>
